  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Providing Opportunities to Women in Ghana</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">A gift to this project is an incredible first step for many women in Ghana, a country with pervasive gender inequality. Our project provides sustainable skills training programs to local women in cooking, sewing and computer skills. Providing a 12-week cycle they join a 6-week program followed by becoming a mentor to a new student for the final 6 weeks. At the end of the 12 weeks, our team build career paths and opportunities for the women. Including small start-up loans from $50.</narrative>
  </description>
